events.title: ⚡ Anon #8724 summons the Lightning of Prosperity!
events.description: The gods smile upon Anon #8724's 2,408.525 offering! Lightning strikes reveal hidden gold veins, technology advances rapidly, and our beautiful civilization leaps forward!

events.title: 🏛️ Gigachad establishes Order of Gigachad Trust!
events.description: With 0.14% ownership of our beautiful civilization, Gigachad is officially recognized as a Notable Citizen and founder of Order of Gigachad Trust! Their bloodline shall guide future generations through the ages. Let this be the beginning of a legendary dynasty!
